f-driven-trucks-safety-driver-bill- assembly-bill-316-autonomous-vehicle</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-09-23T14:03:48-04:00</published><updated> 2023-09-23T14:03:48-04:00</updated><title>最新一代 Apple Watch Series 8 今日起售价低至 279 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Series 8 锻炼应用程序中的心率区屏幕&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/nn96dV-BHS5N5pejmF0ZpeeyiKg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72680849/226266_APPLE_WATCH_8_SE_PHO_akrales_0059.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Apple Watch Series 8 与今年的型号非常相似（惊喜，惊喜）。&lt;/ EM>; |摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;hH05Mu&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23878981/apple-watch-series-9- ultra-2-review-double-tap- precision-finding-siri&quot;>;Apple Watch Series 9&lt;/a>; 已正式登陆，带来了一些细微的改进，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/23786155/watchos-10-preview-apple-watch&quot;>;watchOS 10&lt;/a>;，以及 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/shortcuts/2017/mar/ 22/millennial-pink-is-the-color-of-now-but-what-exactly-is-it&quot;>;新千禧粉红色（！）&lt;/a>;颜色。这款新款智能手表&lt;em>;在技术上&lt;/em>;是苹果有史以来制造的最好的产品，尽管更新都是相当迭代的。值得庆幸的是，如果您想第一次购买 Apple Watch 或从早期型号升级，&lt;strong>;上一代 Series 8&lt;/strong>; 是&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl .me/ckD7BU2RngD&quot;>;百思买有售&lt;/a>;，精选款式起价 279 美元（120 美元）或&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Watch-Midnight-Aluminum-Always/ dp/B0BDHQD1CQ/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊售价 20 美元以上&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c- float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;ncabK8&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;如何安装 watchOS 10 &quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23879092/watchos-10-install-how-to&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple iPhone 15 事件：